# Approved Technology Stack

This project is intentionally minimal. **Use only the technologies below.**
Do NOT add new frameworks, libraries, or dependencies without explicit approval.

## Core stack (installed — do not downgrade)

| Technology | Version / role |
|------------|----------------|
| Next.js | 16.x — App Router, SSR, ISR, route handlers |
| React | 19.x — UI components |
| TypeScript | 5.7 — type-safe codebase |
| Tailwind CSS | 4.x (`@tailwindcss/postcss`) — styling |
| Node.js | ≥ 20.11 — runtime |

## Approved dependencies

- `lucide-react` — icons
- `zod` — schema validation
- `server-only` — server module guard
- `sharp` — build-time image processing (scripts only)

## Architecture rules

- **No database.** All content comes from static TypeScript data in
  `src/lib/static-data/**` + slug resolution. Do not add an ORM, DB client, or
  runtime data store.
- **App Router only** (`src/app/**`). Server Components by default; add
  `"use client"` only for interactive UI.
- **SEO is programmatic**: metadata API, JSON-LD schema, sitemap index +
  sharded urlsets, `robots.ts`.
- **Styling**: Tailwind utilities first; `globals.css` only for what Tailwind
  can't express.

## Before adding anything new

Prefer a built-in Next.js / React feature or existing util. If a new dependency
seems necessary, ask first and explain why nothing already installed works.
